### Test Environment
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@correlationId = demo-trace-001

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
### Sales Audit - New Sale
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/sales
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "employeeId": "emp-001",
  "employeeName": "Developer 4",
  "ticketId": "ticket-001",
  "eventId": "event-001",
  "amount": 45000,
  "paymentMethod": "cash"
}

###
### Ticket Print - First Print
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/tickets/prints
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "employeeId": "emp-001",
  "ticketId": "ticket-001",
  "printerName": "HP-LaserJet-001",
  "reason": "Customer requested physical copy"
}

###
### Ticket Reprint - Duplicate Copy
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/tickets/reprints
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "employeeId": "emp-001",
  "ticketId": "ticket-001",
  "printerName": "HP-LaserJet-001",
  "reason": "Customer lost original, reissuing"
}

###
### Ticket Cancellation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/tickets/cancellations
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: demo-trace-002

{
  "employeeId": "emp-001",
  "ticketId": "ticket-001",
  "reason": "Customer refund request"
}

###
### Get Ticket History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/tickets/ticket-001
X-Correlation-ID: demo-trace-003

###
### Another Sale (Different Employee)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audit/sales
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: demo-trace-004

{
  "employeeId": "emp-002",
  "employeeName": "Assistant Dev 4",
  "ticketId": "ticket-002",
  "eventId": "event-002",
  "amount": 50000,
  "paymentMethod": "credit_card"
}
